{"id": "1431695221720350850", "channel_id": "1431695221720350850", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "随着两周年版本临近，为了让更多守密人能够更顺畅的跟上最新的故事，我们决定在V2.4中做出一些调整。\n\n- 下调忘却篇第四章到第八章的推荐等级。将从 40/50/54/58/60 下调为 35/40/45/50/55。而整个忘却篇困难模式则从 25-80 下调为 25-70。\n\n- 同时我们还将简化第六章到终章的融灾黑潮效果，并为每章引入一定特定界域的增强效果。这些效果将大幅减少各项限制，并带来一定增强。\n\n- 我们还会重新调整第八章与终章的共鸣效果，确保这些效果更容易被使用，并进一步下调敌人的强度。\n\n- 请注意这些内容只是更新中的一小部份，并且可能做出进一步调整。\n\nWith the 2nd-anniversary version approaching, to help more Keepers catch up with the latest story more smoothly, we’ve decided to make some adjustments in V2.4.\n\n- Lowering the recommended levels for Faded Legacy Chapters 4–8. They will be adjusted from 40/50/54/58/60 to 35/40/45/50/55. The overall difficulty mode for the Faded Legacy will also be adjusted from 25–80 down to 25–70.\n\n- We will also simplify the D-tide effects from Chapter 6 to the Finale, and introduce certain Realm-specific enhancement effects for each chapter. These effects will significantly reduce various restrictions and provide certain boosts.\n\n- We will rework the resonance effects in Chapter 8 and the Finale to ensure they’re easier to utilize, and we will further reduce enemy strength.\n\n- Please note the above is only a small portion of the update; details are subject to change.", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T17:25:40.469000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-25T17:37:28.168000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 90}, {"emoji": "👁️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 14}, {"emoji": "💖", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "🫃", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}, {"emoji": "proud", "emoji_id": "1400771683664658433", "count": 6}, {"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "please", "emoji_id": "1356053110375714817", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "⬆️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431695221720350850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：V2.4 忘却篇主线调整 Preview: V2.4 Faded Legacy Main Story Adjustments", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
