{"id": "1431696753710858333", "channel_id": "1431695221720350850", "type": 19, "author_id": "266879563102027777", "author_name": ".vistar", "author_bot": false, "content": "why? legacy chapters are super easy anyways <:Stare:1400771552542199902>", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T17:31:45.724000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431695221720350850", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431695221720350850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：V2.4 忘却篇主线调整 Preview: V2.4 Faded Legacy Main Story Adjustments", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1431697181550579936", "channel_id": "1431695221720350850", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "我们很清楚游戏的独特魅力之一来源于挑战，但我们认为V1.X后期内容的难度过于陡峭，不再适合当前的成长节奏。并且困难模式和其他内容仍然富有挑战。我们也会确保对应推荐等级下仍然能够传递出必要的思考压迫感。\n\nWe’re well aware that one of the game’s unique charms comes from its challenge. However, we believe the late-game difficulty in V1.X spiked too sharply and no longer fits the current progression pace. That said, Hard Mode and other content will remain challenging. We’ll also ensure that, at the corresponding recommended levels, the game still conveys the necessary sense of pressure and thoughtful decision-making.", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T17:33:27.729000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 25}, {"emoji": "sleep1", "emoji_id": "1356053155405762570", "count": 4}, {"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431695221720350850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：V2.4 忘却篇主线调整 Preview: V2.4 Faded Legacy Main Story Adjustments", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
