{"id": "1431699695738032128", "channel_id": "1431695221720350850", "type": 19, "author_id": "1177264312889380935", "author_name": "albomboklat", "author_bot": false, "content": "Kathigu-Ra doesn't mean anything in english and the name is based on Cthugha, a fictional deity from the Cthulhu Mythos horror fiction, an eldritch ball of fire that is basically the elemental spirit of fire and Ra, the egyptian God of the Sun.", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T17:43:27.158000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["877511774834917427"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431699317378257059", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431695221720350850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：V2.4 忘却篇主线调整 Preview: V2.4 Faded Legacy Main Story Adjustments", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
